//TODO: Write Component to hold (Undirected) Graph

import { AspectRatio } from "@mui/icons-material"
import { Container } from "@mui/system"
import Graph from "react-graph-vis"

const GraphBox = (props) => {
    const {graph, options, events, style, getNetwork} = props
    return (
        <Container
        variant="outlined"
        sx={{ width: 300, borderRadius: 'md', overflow: 'auto' }}
        >
        <AspectRatio>
        <Sheet
  variant="outlined"
  sx={{ width: 300, borderRadius: 'md', overflow: 'auto' }}
>
  <AspectRatio>
    <Typography level="h2" component="div">
      16/9
    </Typography>
  </AspectRatio>
</Sheet>
        {/* <Graph graph={graph} options={options} events={events} style={{height: '100%'}} getNetwork={getNetwork}/> */}
        </AspectRatio>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default GraphBox
